		<img class="lconnSprite lconnSprite-iconWarning16" src="https://www-304.ibm.com/connections/resources/web/com.ibm.lconn.core.styles.oneui3/images/blank.gif?etag=20140830.055338" alt="Warning icon" /><span class="lotusAltText">Warning icon</span><span name="message"></span>
